<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lounge Literário</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #fdfaf5; color: #4b3621; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        .navbar-topo { background-color: #4b3621; color: white; padding: 15px 40px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; position: relative; }
        .logo-tipo { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 1.4rem; }
        
        /* Estilo do Menu Dropdown */
        .menu-dropdown {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 60px;
            left: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 1000;
            border-radius: 4px;
            min-width: 150px;
        }

        .menu-dropdown a, .menu-dropdown button {
            color: #4b3621;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        }

        .menu-dropdown a:hover, .menu-dropdown button:hover { background-color: #f1f1f1; }

        /* Estilo do Modal da Biblioteca */
        .modal-biblioteca {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 2000;
            left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: #fdfaf5;
            margin: 5% auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            color: #4b3621;
        }

        .creator-img { width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 2px solid #4b3621; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="navbar-topo">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; cursor: pointer;" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</div>
        
        <div id="myDropdown" class="menu-dropdown">
    
            <button onclick="openModal()">Biblioteca</button>
        </div>

        <div class="logo-tipo text-uppercase">Lounge Literário</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.8rem;"></div>
    </header>

    <div id="infoModal" class="modal-biblioteca">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2 style="font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;">Nossa Biblioteca</h2>
            <hr>
            <p><strong>Data de Criação:</strong> 05 de Abril de 2026</p>
            <p><strong>Motivação:</strong> Em um mundo dominado por vídeos de 15 segundos e algoritmos que decidem o que devemos ver, decidimos criar um santuário. Nossa biblioteca nasceu da vontade de resgatar o prazer de se perder em uma história longa, profunda e eterna, provando que a nossa geração ainda sabe valorizar o peso de uma boa narrativa.</p>
            
            <h4 style="font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; margin-top: 20px;">Criadores:</h4>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-around text-center mt-3">
                <div>
                    <img src="~/img/autor1.jpeg" class="creator-img" alt="Criador 1">
                    <p><em>Emanuelly Lopes</em></p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="~/img/autor2.jpeg" class="creator-img" alt="Criador 2">
                    <p>Maike Souza</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <button class="btn btn-dark mt-4 w-100" style="background: #4b3621;" onclick="closeModal()">FECHAR</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main>
        @RenderBody()
    </main>

    <script>
        
        function toggleMenu() {
            var dropdown = document.getElementById("myDropdown");
            dropdown.style.display = dropdown.style.display === "block" ? "none" : "block";
        }

        
        window.onclick = function(event) {
            if (!event.target.matches('div')) {
                var dropdown = document.getElementById("myDropdown");
                if (dropdown.style.display === "block") {
                    dropdown.style.display = "none";
                }
            }
        }

        
        function openModal() {
            document.getElementById("infoModal").style.display = "block";
            document.getElementById("myDropdown").style.display = "none";
        }

        function closeModal() {
            document.getElementById("infoModal").style.display = "none";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>